<title type="html"><![CDATA[11/13(Sat.)Royal in Banqiao celebrate new meeting venue and on- site meeting re-opening.(Host:Amy)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=558&amp;p=581#p581"><![CDATA[
11/13(Sat.)Royal in Banqiao celebrate new meeting venue and on- site meeting re-opening.(Host:Amy)<br /><br /><span style="color: #FF0000">NEWS !Banqiao Club On-site Meeting Reopening ~  <br /><br />Starting Date:<br />11/13, Saturday<br />7:00-9:00pm<br /><br />New Location Address:<br />新北市板橋區民生路二段120號1F ~(莊敬公園內莊敬市民活動中心）<br /> C Meeting Room <br />新埔捷運站3號出口，直走4-5分鐘<br />Please bring your own drink, the venue  has hot/cold water dispenser, but  doesn't sale any food and drink. <br /><br />Entry fee: <br />NT$ 20 / each person</span><br />--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br /><span style="color: #FF0000"><blockquote class="uncited"><div><br />As a reminder, the seats of gathering on 11/13 are filled already. Thanks for your support.<br /></div></blockquote></span><br /><br /><span style="color: #0000FF">This is the member who has signed up. This is the list below.<br />We will offer snacks (muffin) to each member who can show up.<br /><br />1. Mei<br />2. Gal<br />3. Danny<br />4. Amy<br />5. William<br />6. Ellen<br />7. Joanne<br />8.  Pinn<br />9.  Lawrence<br />10.Lisa<br />11. Andrew<br />12. Wendy              <br />13. Maggie <br />14. Kelvin<br />15. James<br />16.Martin<br />17. George<br />18.May<br />19. Michael H.<br />20. Alan H</span><br /><br />--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />The agenda of the coming Saturday are as belows:  <br /><br />1st  section -7:00-8:00 pm<br />Split into sub-groups for questions &amp; answers<br />(The host will prepare the questions. )<br /><br />2nd section 8:00-8:40 pm<br /><br />1.Self-introductions<br />2. Sharing your special experiences of the pandemic  level 3 at home or in the office.<br /><br />3rd section. 8:40-9:00 pm<br /><br />Joke sharing, singing or dancing etc.<br />------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Thu Nov 11, 2021 9:29 am</p><hr />
